thread.title_full: Alpha Flight Guru reviewed by Dr skw

author: Dr skw
title: Dr skw
text: My guru, Gary Ginsberg has arranged multiple trips for me. All have been flawless and considerably cheaper than the going published rate. I have used other services similar to alpha flight guru and they always tried to put me on crummy airlines. Gary does exactly what I desire ... it may be a bit more but certainly not the "rack rate"
